{
  "id": "69b7a7a3cbc4bc5d0cb4cc7e",
  "title": "母音",
  "created": 1773643686,
  "updated": 1773644980,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b7a7a3cbc4bc5d0cb4cc7e",
      "text": "母音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643686,
      "updated": 1773643686
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a7a50000000000551e99",
      "text": "母音を調音する際に舌を盛り上げる位置の前後・上下と唇を丸めないか丸めるかで区別される",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643686,
      "updated": 1773643776
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a80a0000000000551e9b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643786,
      "updated": 1773643786
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a80b0000000000551e9c",
      "text": "table:母音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643787,
      "updated": 1773643793
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a8110000000000551e9d",
      "text": " \t前舌\t準前舌\t中舌\t準後舌\t後舌",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643793,
      "updated": 1773644131
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a81f0000000000551e9e",
      "text": " 狭\ti • y\t\tɨ • ʉ\t\tɯ • u\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643807,
      "updated": 1773643883
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a81f0000000000551ea1",
      "text": " 広めの狭\t\tɪ • ʏ\tɪ̈ • ʊ̈\tɯ̽ • ʊ\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643807,
      "updated": 1773643902
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a81f0000000000551ea2",
      "text": " 半狭\te • ø\t\tɘ • ɵ\t\tɤ • o\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643807,
      "updated": 1773643911
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a81f0000000000551ea3",
      "text": " 中央\te̞ • ø̞\t\tə • ɵ̞\t\tɤ̞ • o̞",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643807,
      "updated": 1773643934
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a81f0000000000551ea4",
      "text": " 半広\tɛ • œ\t\tɜ • ɞ\t\tʌ • ɔ\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643807,
      "updated": 1773643945
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a81f0000000000551ea5",
      "text": " 狭めの広\tæ • \t\tɐ • ɞ̞\t\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643807,
      "updated": 1773643983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a81f0000000000551ea6",
      "text": " 広\ta • ɶ\t\tä\t\tɑ • ɒ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643807,
      "updated": 1773643995
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a7ae0000000000551e9a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773643695,
      "updated": 1773643695
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7aa2b0000000000551ecb",
      "text": "準前舌と準後舌の区分を廃止すると表としての見た目が綺麗になる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644332,
      "updated": 1773644483
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7aa2b0000000000551ecc",
      "text": "table:母音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644332,
      "updated": 1773644389
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7aa640000000000551ecd",
      "text": " \t前舌\t中舌\t後舌",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644389,
      "updated": 1773644432
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7aa640000000000551ece",
      "text": " 狭\ti • y\tɨ • ʉ\tɯ • u",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644389,
      "updated": 1773644434
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7aa640000000000551ecf",
      "text": " 広めの狭\tɪ • ʏ\tɪ̈ • ʊ̈\tɯ̽ • ʊ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644389,
      "updated": 1773644435
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7aa640000000000551ed0",
      "text": " 半狭\te • ø\tɘ • ɵ\tɤ • o",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644389,
      "updated": 1773644436
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7aa640000000000551ed1",
      "text": " 中央\te̞ • ø̞\tə • ɵ̞\tɤ̞ • o̞",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644389,
      "updated": 1773644428
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7aa640000000000551ed2",
      "text": " 半広\tɛ • œ\tɜ • ɞ\tʌ • ɔ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644389,
      "updated": 1773644438
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7aa640000000000551ed3",
      "text": " 狭めの広\tæ • \tɐ • ɞ̞\t",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644389,
      "updated": 1773644427
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7aa640000000000551ed4",
      "text": " 広\ta • ɶ\tä\tɑ • ɒ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644389,
      "updated": 1773644426
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7aa640000000000551ed5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644389,
      "updated": 1773644389
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a9ba0000000000551ec8",
      "text": "更に母音の長短の区別を持つ場合がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644219,
      "updated": 1773644249
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a9d90000000000551eca",
      "text": "更に二重母音・三重母音を持つ場合がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644249,
      "updated": 1773644267
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7a9d20000000000551ec9",
      "text": "最も区別が少ない言語では概ね a i u の 3 音が区別される。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644244,
      "updated": 1773644980
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7ac890000000000551ed7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773644938,
      "updated": 1773644938
    }
  ]
}